2.1 State is contextual

A reader may inhabit different states in different domains. Someone can be a Steward of one constellation and an Initiate in another.

2.2 State is not linear

Progress may involve:

gaining a concept

losing an assumption

recovering uncertainty

revisiting an earlier symbol with deeper understanding

becoming less certain but more capable

Regression may be a necessary movement before integration.

