9.1 Evidence strength

Level

Signal

Echo

The reader repeats the language.

Recognition

The reader identifies the pattern elsewhere.

Application

The reader uses the frame in a decision or creation.

Transfer

The capability works in a new domain.

Coordination

Multiple agents use the frame to act together.

Reality contact

An external result changes measurably.

Mutation

Evidence causes the repository itself to evolve.

Pantheon should distinguish semantic resonance from external validation without dismissing either.

